Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 00:33:18 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Enable yhteenvetoilmoitus (EU sales summary) for local SQLite
 databases

Previously the feature was gated behind a cloud connectivity check,
preventing users with local databases from generating the declaration.

- Add /alv/eu route handler to AlvRoute for local SQLite databases
- Remove PilviModel guard in AlvSivu::pyydaYhteenvetoTiedot()
- Use toimituspvm from invoice JSON for period filtering, matching
  Vero's requirement that service delivery date determines the
  reporting period (not the invoice date)
- Handle NULL debit/credit values in the SQL query
---
 kitsas/alv/alvsivu.cpp            | 12 +++---
 kitsas/sqlite/routes/alvroute.cpp | 62 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 kitsas/sqlite/routes/alvroute.h   |  3 ++
 3 files changed, 69 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

